headline: Waters Corporation to Present at the TD Cowen Health Care Conference
summary: Waters Corporation (NYSE:WAT) announced that Udit Batra, Ph.D., Waters President and Chief Executive Officer, will participate in a fireside chat at the TD Cowen Health Care Conference on Monday, March 2nd, 2026, at 11:10 AM Eastern Time.
